data.description: Make this your first and last stop of the day! This beautiful home is situated on a beautiful lot within the Hillpoint Estates community located in Suffolk. Beautiful vinyl floors, carpet, custom light fixtures, a large master bathroom with double sinks and a spacious walk-in closet. This home also offers a beautiful updated kitchen that includes granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. A tankless water heater, dual-zoned hvac system and a cozy fireplace in the living room also adds peace of mind. The only thing that is missing from this home is YOU.
